

 Meta Package Handle



RPM - 
    ------> dependency ( means to install specific software, you need  other software as well and that is because many problems are using libraries.


Solution to dependency is ---> Meta Handler --> a web server or a repository where installer looks for  dependeny.

on Redhat --> Meta package handler is yum.
On Debian --> Meta package handler is apt
on Suse --> Meta package handler is zypper
